eventText: Parag replied back to Philipp on sponsor slider options.
Parag checked all the sponsor sliders and replied back to Nana.
Pranav asks Bettina to provide he required graphical information ( Tool information   Home screen icon )  for PLL guideline
Pranav sends the content images of PLL guideline from DGK app.
Shaishav sends email that CPP will remain in the same style. Shaishav asked for developers. Sambhaji replied names as Shrinath, Piyush
For Nichtkardiale GL, Bettina sends the required graphical information to Pranav.
Bettina tells us that for PLL Aottenerkrankungen, Carla is responsible and to contact Carla for this guideline.
Pranav has sent email to Carla to send graphical information on PLL Aottenerkrankungen guideline.
Bettina has sent email, that one mistake in the VHF GL in DGK app. When can update this page? Sambhaji is asking for mistake.
Gaurav contacts Bettina for GLs that go in the next technical update. Gaurav also wants to know about tools.
Gaurav informs Bettina that, for Nichtkardiale GL, GL export is almost done but pending due to some issues regarding orphan paragraph
Pranav contacts Carla on PLL guideline graphical information.
Shaishav sends the DGK CPP tool for checking.
Gaurav sends a gentle reminder to Bettina to resolve the TOC issue in Nichtkardiale guideline.
Parag explains Nathalie that adding icon on homescreen and adding landing page will be too much work for us. This also includes technical update of DGK app.
Philipp says, for now we go with the "slider before each tool“ option. Marc will make the POC.
Bettina sends the corrected TOC to Gaurav for Nichtkardiale guideline.
Bettina finishes all the changes for VHF, sambhaji forwards the info to wen production, production programming
Bettina sends a list of guidelines for next technical update.
Vaclav is asking Bettina for deadlines of 4 guidelines in the DGK app.
Disha uploads the CPP on ITD and informs Shaishav to check.
Nichtkardiale guideline is now on CMS. Gaurav informs Bettina.
Gaurav informs that the Nichtkardiale guideline is on CMS. Bettina acknowledges that the she is checking guideline on CMS.
Shaishav sends some more files to replace in DGK CPP to Disha.
Sambhaji forwards the modules programming team feedback to Ben.
Disha sends email to Shaishav that, she has updated the tool on ITD. Shaishav can check the updated tool on CMS Viewer app.
Pranav contacts Marc for icons design on home screen. Also sends the character restrictions on icon to Ben.
Bettina is not able to see the tools in the CMS viewer app. Gaurav has made the fix. Bettina can now see the tools in CMS Viewer app.
Constance sends the source files for DGK app. Pranav updates the static images and sends it to programmers. Sambhaji forwards the images to Constance for approvals.
Gaurav informs Carla that the PLL Aortenerkrankungen GL is now available on CMS.
Bettina approves that only two page can be pushed in VHF guideline for now, DYSLIp tools can come later.
Pranav contacts Marc for open files of one new guideline for CPPs.
Marc replies that he will send the open files today.
Sambhaji gives the confirmation to Shrinath and Piyush to push the two pages in the online app.
Server update in DGK app for two page pushed by Shrinath, Piyush
Gaurav requests Carla to send information on tools in PLL guideline.
Carla sends the .mrf file for PLL guideline to Gaurav.
Marc sends the first draft of icons to Pranav. Marc awaits feedbacks from Ben.
Sandra tells that the Daichi Sankyo extended the slider contract for VHF. Please keep the slider online.
Gaurav has linked one algo to content, informs Carla. Gaurav informs that footer is missing and Disha will work on the changes later.
Ben has approved the icons and splash screen for CPP.
Carla will work on Monday to activate the footer buttons in algomaker.
Carla informs Gaurav that she has added the footer section in one algo in PLL guideline.
Marc has finalised the app icons and Pranav will take care of providing it to the programmers. Sambhaji has asked Ben to provide the information on flip images for 6 CPPs.
Pranav sends the proposal of splash screen and icons to Ben and Marc.
Gaurav informs Bettina that CMS Viewer app do not support FFC.
Ben sends back the changes in splash screen and icons.
Pranav makes the changes and sends it back to Ban for approval.
Ben sends the information required for new CPU CPP guidelines on CMS.
Bettina informs that, Kardiovaskuläre Komplikationen… is now approved from Authors.
Sambhaji asks Bettina, whether Perikarderkrankungen guideline is also approved.
Bettina says Perikarderkrankungen guideline is already approved.
Pranav has asked for DD, Marc will send it after discussion with Mariona.
Mariona sends the design draft @7Mar after making changes. Also sends the open files to Pranav.
Pranav sends email to Mariona pointing the font error and icons discrepancies.
Mariona replies to Pranav and provide information on fonts.
Pranav sends the graphics data to programmers.
